      <title>由於 Netflix、晶片股拖累，納斯達克指數落後於同業；美國運通提振道瓊指數</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-streets-fear-gauge-over-5-month-high-rate-cut-mideast-worries-2024-04-19/</link>
